{{Infobox video game | collapsible = | state = | italic title = | title = A Bastard's Tale | image = ABastard'sTaleImg.jpg | alt = | caption = | developer = No Pest Productions | publisher = No Pest Productions | series = | engine = | platforms = [[PlayStation 4]], [[Microsoft Windows]] | released = {{Unbulleted list|'''Microsoft Windows''' |May 28, 2015| '''PlayStation 4''' |October 4, 2016}}<ref name="3S"/><ref name="IGN"/> | genre = [[Action-adventure game|Action-adventure]] | modes = | director = | producer = | designer = | programmer = | artist = | writer = | composer = | cabinet = | arcade system = | cpu = | sound = | display = }} '''''A Bastard's Tale''''' is an [[Action game|action]] [[2D computer graphics|2D]] [[video game]], published by Swedish studio No Pest Productions for [[PlayStation 4]] and [[Microsoft Windows]].<ref name="IGN">{{cite web |url= http://www.ign.com/games/a-bastards-tale |title= A Bastard's Tale |website= ign.com |publisher= IGN |access-date= 2018-09-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180911081927/http://www.ign.com/games/a-bastards-tale |archive-date= 2018-09-11 |dead-url= no |df= }}</ref><ref name="MC">{{cite web |url= https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/a-bastards-tale |title= A Bastard's Tale |website= metacritic.com |publisher= Metacritic |access-date= 2018-09-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170915003609/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/a-bastards-tale |archive-date= 2017-09-15 |dead-url= no |df= }}</ref><ref name="Steam">{{cite web |url= https://store.steampowered.com/app/371550/A_Bastards_Tale/ |title= A Bastard's Tale |website= steampowered.com |publisher= STEAM |access-date= 2018-09-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180911081943/https://store.steampowered.com/app/371550/A_Bastards_Tale/ |archive-date= 2018-09-11 |dead-url= no |df= }}</ref><ref name="3S">{{cite web |url= http://3rd-strike.com/a-bastards-tale-review/ |title= A Bastard's Tale – Review |website= 3rd-strike.com |publisher= 3rd STRIKE |access-date= 2018-09-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180911114305/http://3rd-strike.com/a-bastards-tale-review/ |archive-date= 2018-09-11 |dead-url= no |df= }}</ref>
==Gameplay== The game features basic pixilated-base graphics and features the player defeating fifteen different enemy characters which are having their own distinct features, throughout five levels.<ref name="3S"/>
