'''''Gai Shanxi and her Sisters''''' ({{zh|c=盖山西和她的姐妹们|p=gai shan xi he ta de jie mei men}}), directed by [[Ban Zhongyi]], is a 2007 [[Cinema of China#New Documentary Movement|independent Chinese documentary]] about a Chinese woman's ordeal as a "[[comfort woman]]" for the [[Imperial Japanese Army|Japanese Army]] during [[World War II]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20061202f1.html| author = Jun Hongo| title= China filmmaker finds wartime sex slaves| publisher = ''[[The Japan Times]]'' | date = 2006-12-02| accessdate=2009-10-28}}</ref>
