'''Imago Theatre''' is a theatre company based in [[Portland, Oregon]], United States.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wweek.com/arts/2016/07/12/after-24-years-an-east-burnside-theater-is-closing/ |title=East Burnside Theater is Closing After 24 Years - Willamette Week |website=Wweek.com |date=2016-07-06 |accessdate=2016-07-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Scott |first=Aaron |url=http://www.opb.org/artsandlife/article/portland-imago-theatre-sell-historic-building/#.V4XSYc389Es.mailto |title=Imago Theatre To Sell Its Historic Portland Building Amid Rising Costs . Arts & Life |publisher=OPB |date= |accessdate=2016-07-15}}</ref> It was founded by Carol Triffle and Jerry Mouawad in 1979.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imagotheatre.com |title=Imago Theatre |publisher=Imago Theatre |date= |accessdate=2016-07-15}}</ref>
